            "body": "OK, dug around:\r\n\r\n* Removed in #1820 \r\n* Partially due to #1124, `--help` wouldn't pick up custom commands due to the order Click would execute things to load the `--app` option.\r\n* Click tracking issue, still open, pallets/click#590\r\n\r\nThis might only apply to `--app`, maybe `--debug` can be added back in?"
